Oracle said: The object is made of fiberglass.	Guesser said: I believe the object is a surfboard.?	Oracle said: No.	Guesser said: What are the dimensions of the object?	Oracle said: The object is typically 20 to 100 meters in length.	Guesser said: I believe the object is a boat.?	Oracle said: Correct.
